    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Alice作为actor，Charlie作为participant。需要体现他们之间的消息传递吗，还是先标注一些背景信息？",
      "elements_involved": [
