    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "先加两个注释吧。在Alice那边标注\"some note\"，说明这是用户触发操作的起点；Charlie那边标注\"other note\"，表示服务端的处理上下文。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "Charlie",
        "note"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，就是在Alice上方加注释\"some note\"，Charlie上方加\"other note\"。这两个note都是覆盖在他们各自的生命线上的对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
