    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了。Alice作为actor在最左侧，Charlie作为participant在右侧，各自上方都有对应的注释框。结构很简洁。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
