      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，Charlie的注释文字确认一下——是\"other note\"不是\"another note\"吧？我刚才说的可能有歧义。",
